ulin, particularly in patients with advanced age and/or renal impairment.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/116041/', '', 'Liraglutide, Lixisenatide', 'Cholestyramine, Rosuvastatin, Mipomersen, Evinacumab, Dextrothyroxine, Simvastatin, Probucol, Cerivastatin, Lomitapide, Ezetimibe, Atorvastatin, More', 1767369485);
